message: If you are in Los Angeles you don't want to miss this! Both films are very powerful!

data.description:
Our films UNSEEN DANCES and TANYA have been selected for the FLICKS4CHANGE Film Festival here in Los Angeles. 

Co-Founder Jordan Marinov will also present a dance she choreographed with dancers from Unseen Dances. 

November 12th - 15th at Boomtown Brewery

To "RSVP," go to: www.flicks4change.eventbrite.com
